title: Get To Work
description:
Get To Work is a punishing, yet satisfying experience about a young man on a mission to conquer the corporate world on rollerblades. Maneuver a slippery character with rollerblades on both his arms and feet that only knows how to move fast. The Witcher 2: Assassins of Kings
With your narrator, Connor ‘CDawgVA’ Colquhoun, to encourage you on your climb to the top, navigate through massive gaps, ramps, jumps, and other devious obstacles trying to bring you down.
